      <p class="text-text-light max-w-[560px] mx-auto leading-[1.8] text-[0.92rem] md:text-base" data-en="A glimpse into the transformations and experiences at SVET MEDICAL." data-ro="O privire asupra transformărilor și experiențelor de la SVET MEDICAL.">A glimpse into the transformations and experiences at SVET MEDICAL.</p>
